# About SwyxKit

SwyxKit is a blog template meant for frontend developers who want to get a performant, fully featured content site up and running with Astro, React, Tailwind CSS, and other modern blog features.

This version has been ported to **Astro + React + Tailwind v4** with complete feature parity. Below is the full README.md from the original SvelteKit version: [https://github.com/sw-yx/swyxkit](https://github.com/sw-yx/swyxkit)

