This version maintains complete feature parity with the original SvelteKit version while leveraging Astro's unique strengths:

- Islands Architecture - Ship only the JavaScript you need
- Local MDX files instead of GitHub Issues CMS
- Modern tooling with TypeScript v5
- Improved build performance and bundle size

